## Common Mistakes

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Sync database calls | Use async SQLAlchemy or asyncpg |
| No request validation | Use Pydantic models for all inputs |
| Hardcoded config | Use pydantic-settings with env vars |
| No error handling | Use exception handlers and HTTPException |
| Blocking in async | Use `run_in_executor` for blocking calls |
| No dependency injection | Use `Depends()` for shared logic |
